(PID.TID 0042.0001) ># Oceanic Williamson TC1 passive-tracer advection.
(PID.TID 0042.0001) ># One-layer, global lat-lon ocean with prescribed solid-body velocity.
(PID.TID 0042.0001) ># ===============================================================
(PID.TID 0042.0001) >
